content: ... That every time you have a king or ace of spades that the last player (to your left) ALWAYS has the queen. All the stuff about AI really doesn't amount to a hill of beans if the game is stacked against you. Pissed me off so much I uninstalled both spades and hearts from this developer, even after paying for both. Such a fundamental error.
replyContent:
We apologise for your frustration but deals really are completely random, 
determined by a random number generator based on your device time in milliseconds. Our engines are backed by serious academic work so unfair play is not an option: see http://www.aifactory.co.uk/AIF_Publications.htm
